{
  "stem": "3933.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were wearing this white arm bands, we started out looking-- going working for the Germans-- not only because of the feudal-- we weren't paid anyway, but maybe-- they were giving us bread.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bread was the main thing, but also perhaps we were telling-- it was told that if you are employed for Germans we will avoid other trouble-- trouble with-- of course, obviously them, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody in there, they called us [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[GERMAN] which means a statement that you are employed in-- in our unit or something, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Even-- even cleaning for them and doing things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now after-- well I find a place where I cleaned and I washed for soldiers, they were stationed in Rovno, where they've got some individual places where they slept, and they were fairly nice to me.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was young and-- and kind of attractive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I learned the language, picked up every word, every word-- I'm very good at languages-- that I picked up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- in daylight they took me with my son, Lieber-- we called him Lieber-- later we changed it, by the way, to Zbyszek.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Zbyshek Z-b-- Z-b-y-s-h-e-k.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we started to go on with those things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a little while, I can't remember, it was very short time, the posters and the rumors, we are going to have to wear yellow [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They call this in Yiddish, [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In German they call this, [GERMAN], I can't-- [GERMAN] isn't German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- they called this [GERMAN], or-- a [GERMAN] means a stain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were removed, they forget about the white arm bands-- was too good to be nice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we're going to wear two of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
